OL,3,CA 'Churchillian' masterpiece:
OL,4,Cpolitician immortalised in paper mache
OL,6,FThe likeness of a Guernsey politician
OL,7,Fhas been captured by the work of a
OL,8,Flocal caricaturist.
OL,10,FDeputy John Gollop's likeness has been
OL,11,Frecreated - in paper mache form - by
OL,12,Fartist Ross le Brun.
OL,14,FRoss says the 'Mini Gollop' was an
OL,15,Fopportunity to practice transferring
OL,16,Fhis caricature skills from paper to
OL,17,Fplaster.
