OL,3,CA 'Churchillian' masterpiece:
OL,4,Cpolitician immortalised in paper mache
OL,6,FRoss adds that he chose a caricature
OL,7,Frather than a 'straight' portrait
OL,8,Fbecause they're instantly recognisable
OL,9,Fand tend to make people smile.
OL,11,FSomething of a local celebrity, Deputy
OL,12,FGollop's statue is unmistakable:
OL,13,Fcomplete with his signature cigarette
OL,14,Fand bag of papers in hand.
OL,16,FDeputy Gollop has given the miniature
OL,17,Fdouble his seal of approval.
OL,19,FHe says: "I think he looks a bit
OL,20,Fyounger and smarter than me in real
OL,21,Flife.
