OL,3,CA 'Churchillian' masterpiece:
OL,4,Cpolitician immortalised in paper mache
OL,6,F"It gives me a bit of Churchillian
OL,7,Fpugnacious look... whether that's
OL,8,FWinston Churchill, or Churchill the
OL,9,Fdog though, I'm not too sure."
OL,11,F'Mini Gollop' is currently being
OL,12,Fexhibited at the George Crossan
OL,13,FGallery as part of the 2024 Guernsey
OL,14,FArts Open.
OL,16,FThe exhibition celebrates the
OL,17,Fdiversity of local talent and
OL,18,Fencourages collaboration between
OL,19,Fartists.
